    "client_msg_id": "117caca8-8ce5-4e93-ba36-0c2111378f50",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Thanks for the great links and feedback! I hadn't actually thought of the rationale you gave for restarts. It makes sense though. A far more tolerable, hence more common, microcosm of the \"try reinstalling Windows\" shrug-of-the-shoulders \"solution\". Too complex to reason about =&gt; destroy everything and start again from scratch, which is at least a well-understood state.\n\nI've just added a short bit to the end I somehow didn't think to include, until a mention of \"aggressively pushed updates\" in the one of the above papers brought up some unpleasant memories and fire in my heart. *Now* it feels officially finished :slightly_smiling_face:",
